  "name": "Automatic Knowledge",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You know basic facts off the top of your head. Choose a skill you're an expert in that has the Recall Knowledge action and for which you have the Assurance feat. You can use the Recall Knowledge action with that skill as a free action once per round. If you do, you must use Assurance on the skill check.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Special</strong> You can select this feat multiple times, choosing a different skill each time. You can use Automatic Knowledge with any skills you have chosen, but you can still use Automatic Knowledge only once per round.</p>"
